  "transcript": [
    {
      "turn": 1,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Hi Priyansh, the 2018 IPL final still gives me chills, Jadhav running, Krunal’s catch, pure *dhamaal*. Any other matches that left you speechless lately?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "The 2020 final was *unbeleivable* too. Virat’s 100, CSK’s chase... still *jaw-dropping*. But yeah, Jadhav’s run in 2018 was *something else*. I think I was *speechless* that day too."
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "\"Got it, 2020 was another wild one. Virat’s 100 was epic, wasn’t it? What’s your most unforgettable cricket moment, a game, a run, or a catch?\""
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "The 2019 World Cup semi-final between India and New Zealand was *unforgettable* for me. That tie, the Super Over... *naa hoga* but it happened! I was watching it with friends, and we were *all in shock*. That was *something else*."
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "\"Right, that World Cup semi final was a shocker, no doubt. Tied, a Super Over, and that final catch by Conway. What made that moment stick with you the most?\""
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "The *drama*, the tension... *unreal*. We were all *speechless* after the Super Over. And Conway’s catch? *Bhai*, I still can’t believe it! It felt like a movie scene."
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "\"That’s the kind of drama movies are made of, and you were right there in the middle of it. What’s another moment that felt like a movie scene for you?\""
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "The 2016 T20 World Cup final between England and Australia had that *movie moment* feel too. Rain delay, Duckworth-Lewis, and that last over *chaos*... *unbelieveable*. I was *on the edge* the whole time."
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "\"Right, that 2016 final had everything, rain, chaos, and a last over thriller. What part of that match sticks out the most for you?\""
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "The *last over* was *crazy*. 5 runs needed off 2 balls, and the tension? *Unreal*. I was *sweating* like it was my own team. And remember, they *won* it — *so cinematic*! But I should probably *wind down*, got some work to do. Catch you later, Maya!"
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "\"Got it, that last over had everyone on their feet. Take your time with work, catch you for another innings soon!\""
    }
  ],
